Class SQLXMLImpl.AdjustingJAXPParser<T extends Adjusting.XML.Parsing<T>>

java.lang.Object
org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc.SQLXMLImpl.AdjustingJAXPParser<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
SQLXMLImpl.AdjustingSourceResult, SQLXMLImpl.AdjustingStAXSource, SQLXMLImpl.AdjustingStreamResult, SQLXMLImpl.SAXDOMCommon
Enclosing class:
SQLXMLImpl<V extends Datum>
abstract static class SQLXMLImpl.AdjustingJAXPParser<T extends Adjusting.XML.Parsing<T>> extends Object implements Adjusting.XML.Parsing<T>
Implements setters for the later JAXP security properties, which use the same names for SAX, StAX, and DOM, so the individual setters can all be here with only the setFirstSupportedProperty method abstract.
